<Layout
  title="Mat Pilates vs Reformer Pilates: Which Should Beginners Start With? | fitness-complete.com"
  description="The honest answer depends on what you actually want from it."
>

  <main>
    <article class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pt-16 pb-20">

      <a href="/blog" class="inline-block text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-600 transition-colors mb-8">← Blog</a>

